<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='288000' id='t-288000'>So I hope you can see.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='290000' id='t-290000'>I really hope you can see how what we're doing here</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='292000' id='t-292000'>is taking a compelling question, a compelling answer,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='294000' id='t-294000'>but we're paving a smooth, straight path</span>
