<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='378000' id='t-378000'>who, I believe, has paid his dues.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='380000' id='t-380000'>He talked about the formulation of a problem being so incredibly important,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='383000' id='t-383000'>and yet in my practice, in the U.S. here,</span>
