</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:42
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='391000' id='t-391000'>So 90 percent of what I do</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='393000' id='t-393000'>with my five hours of prep time per week</span>
