<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='476000' id='t-476000'>And that question, off this right here, is really fun for me</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='479000' id='t-479000'>because, like the intro,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='481000' id='t-481000'>I teach kids -- because of my inexperience --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='484000' id='t-484000'>I teach the kids that are the most remedial, all right?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='486000' id='t-486000'>And I've got kids who will not join a conversation about math</span>
