</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:15
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='544000' id='t-544000'>So I'm here to report some really fun games</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='546000' id='t-546000'>with students who come pre-installed</span>
