<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='573000' id='t-573000'>This has been a lot of fun.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:46
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='575000' id='t-575000'>I encourage math teachers I talk to to use multimedia,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='578000' id='t-578000'>because it brings the real world into your classroom</span>
